high_descs: turn left, go forward to left side of black round table
pick up black bowl on dining table
turn right, go to refrigerator to the left
place black bowl on top shelf of refrigerator, close refrigerator, open refrigerator, pick up black bowl from top shelf of refrigerator, close refrigerator
turn right, open cabinet door to the left of the stove
place black bowl in cabinet, close cabinet door
anns.task_desc: Place chilled black bowl in cabinet to the left of stove

high_descs: Turn and go to the table on the side that is closest to the door.
Pick up the bowl that is on the table.
With the bowl in hand turn and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the bowl on the top shelf.  Close the door. Open the fridge and take the bowl out that is on the top shelf.
With bowl in hand turn around so you are facing the cabinet that is to the right of the fridge.
Open the lower cabinet and place the bowl in the cabinet.  Closet the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl in fridge and then in cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn right, then go straight to approach the table, then turn right.
Pick up the bowl on the table, to the left of the soap.
Turn around, move straight, turn left, move forward, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge.
Turn around, go forward, turn left, go forward, then turn left to face the cabinet next to the fridge.
Put the bowl in the cabinet next to the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the cold bowl in the cabinet.
